405
00:27:35,528 --> 00:27:37,972
Saya percaya Anda, GM, dan semua staf.

406
00:27:37,972 --> 00:27:40,258
Kami selalu bersamamu!

407
00:27:40,258 --> 00:27:41,976
Begitu pula dengan Prez.

408
00:27:41,976 --> 00:27:43,294
Saya juga.

409
00:27:43,294 --> 00:27:44,928
Itulah yang ingin kami dengar!

410
00:27:46,870 --> 00:27:51,059
Tolong izinkan kami membantu semampu kami.

411
00:27:51,059 --> 00:27:52,111
Benar kan?

412
00:27:52,111 --> 00:27:53,387
Ya, tuan!

413
00:27:53,387 --> 00:27:55,055
Baiklah, ayo pergi!

414
00:27:56,630 --> 00:27:59,993
Terima kasih banyak semuanya!

415
00:28:04,119 --> 00:28:05,791
Halo!
[Tolong dukung Mimpi]

416
00:28:05,791 --> 00:28:08,097
Tolong pinjamkan kekuatanmu pada Mimpi.
